name: JK Tight Bikini Top [Underboob + Skindentation]
description:
Sometimes a bikini top can be too tight, can't it?

The updated version of this project can only be found on JK Patreon.

LoRA prompt weight: 0.5 (short prompting) to 0.8 (long prompting)
Model used for training: Uber Realistic Porn Merge 1.3. SD stock VAE

You can use any color on bikini (as shown in the example). But this model have a tendency to close-up on breasts. To solve this, use some prompts to emphasize the face, like "beautiful face", "symmetric face", "makeup" and/or a famous face. Use this on neg: breast focus.

This lora also has a tendency to enlarge breasts, you can use "big breasts" on neg to resolve.

See my other LoRAs:

Inverted Nipples

Puffy Nipples

Perfect Perky Breasts

Dude, how I would like to see a "too small bikini" now.
